OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FResults from Jersey's Election were
OL,7,Fannounced overnight on Sunday evening
OL,8,F(June 7), with some groups enjoying
OL,9,Fsubstantial gains while the island's
OL,10,Fbiggest party, Reform Jersey, is
OL,11,Fsignificantly weakened.
OL,13,FThousands of voters took to the polls
OL,14,Fto pick nine Senators, 28 Deputies and
OL,15,F12 Constables to represent them over
OL,16,Fthe next four years.
OL,18,FSo who are this year's big winners and
OL,19,Flosers, and why are we seeing such a
OL,20,Fshift?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
