OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FReform Jersey
OL,8,FReform Jersey describes itself as a
OL,9,Fsocial democratic party, highlighting
OL,10,F"that it is the duty of the state, in
OL,11,Fpartnership with its citizens, to help
OL,12,Fcreate a society that works for all,
OL,13,Fincluding the poorest and most
OL,14,Fdisadvantaged."
OL,16,FFounded as a pressure group in 2012 to
OL,17,Fcampaign for electoral reform, it
OL,18,Fofficially registered as a political
OL,19,Fparty in 2014 to compete in that
OL,20,Fyear's general election.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
