OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781100697
OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FIn 2022, Reform secured 10 seats,
OL,7,Fdoubling their returns from the
OL,8,Fprevious election in 2018.
OL,10,FDuring this term, Reform Jersey passed
OL,11,Fa new Residential Tenancy Law,
OL,12,Fabolished the fee for children and
OL,13,Ffull-time students to see a GP, and
OL,14,Fexpanded free childcare by providing
OL,15,F15 hours of free care a week for
OL,16,Fchildren aged 2 to 3.
OL,18,FFar from building on their successes,
OL,19,Fthe party has only secured seven seats
OL,20,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
