OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FThe seven are: Deputy Tom Coles (St
OL,7,FHelier South), Deputy Catherine Curtis
OL,8,F(St Helier Central), Deputy Lyndsay
OL,9,FFeltham (St Helier Central), Deputy
OL,10,FBeatriz Poree (St Helier South),
OL,11,FDeputy Monty Tadier (St Brelade),
OL,12,FDeputy Carina Alves (St Helier
OL,13,FCentral), Deputy Lee Carpenter (St
OL,14,FHelier Central).
OL,16,FSam Mezec who was first elected as a
OL,17,FDeputy in 2014 when he was just 23,
OL,18,Fhas lost his seat- leaving Reform
OL,19,FJersey without their leader.
OL,26,@rD@LrrxD@Frr
