OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FHe came 10th in the race to become one
OL,7,Fof the the island's Senators, missing
OL,8,Fout by one place as the top nine are
OL,9,Felected.
OL,11,FAnother Reform Jersey candidate who
OL,12,Fwas unsuccessful in this year's
OL,13,Felection is Rob Ward, the former
OL,14,FMinister of Education.
OL,16,FReacting to the results, Sam Mezec
OL,17,Fsaid:
OL,26,@xD@_rr
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/13
