OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,F"It wasn't the result we were hoping
OL,7,Ffor, but I am immensely grateful to
OL,8,Feveryone who voted for me and
OL,9,Fsupported me in my time as a States
OL,10,FMember over the years.
OL,12,F"I am incredibly proud of all of
OL,13,FReform Jersey's achievements in that
OL,14,Ftime, including expanding free child
OL,15,Fcare to 2-3 year olds, consistently
OL,16,Fmaking primary healthcare more
OL,17,Faffordable for more groups of
OL,18,Fislanders and establishing a first
OL,19,Ftime buyer policy.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
