OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,F"My strongest legacy will be the new
OL,7,FResidential Tenancy Law, which will
OL,8,Fcontinue to protect the tenants I've
OL,9,Ffought so far for from revenge
OL,10,Fevictions and unjustifiable rent hikes
OL,11,Ffor years to come.
OL,13,F"It will now be the job of the new
OL,14,Fleadership of Reform Jersey to take
OL,15,Four movement forward. It remains the
OL,16,Fonly vehicle through which ordinary
OL,17,Fislanders will ever truly have their
OL,18,Finterests represented in the States.
OL,20,FValue Jersey
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
