OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FValue Jersey is a self-described
OL,7,F"voluntary organisation, created by
OL,8,Fislanders and funded by islanders."
OL,9,FThe group's primary focus is on
OL,10,Ftackling the cost of living crisis,
OL,11,Fand making Jersey more affordable.
OL,13,FWhile not a political party itself,
OL,14,Fnine candidates endorsed the group's
OL,15,F'Purple Book' of policies and
OL,16,Fobjectives ahead of the election. This
OL,17,Fincludes calls to cut government waste
OL,18,Fand save the local economy, while
OL,19,Fkeeping taxes low.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
