OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1781100697
OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FSix of these nine candidates were
OL,7,Felected. These include Gabriel
OL,8,FRaimondo, who becomes the youngest
OL,9,Fparliamentarian in the world at 18
OL,10,Fyears old, and Serena Kersten Guthrie,
OL,11,Fthe former captain of England's
OL,12,Fnetball team and now one of the
OL,13,Fisland's nine elected Senators.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/13
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
