OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FDespite the success of candidates who
OL,7,Fhave endorsed Value Jersey's Purple
OL,8,FBook, Samantha Gleave, a newly elected
OL,9,FDeputy for St Helier South, says the
OL,10,Fgroup will not be celebrating the
OL,11,Fresults. Instead, they will be
OL,12,F"looking at the other (candidates) and
OL,13,Fthinking how they can get them onboard
OL,14,Fwith also delivering the policies that
OL,15,Fare going to tackle the cost of living
OL,16,Fcrisis for islanders."
OL,26,@tD@WpmtD@bpn
