OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,FThe six elected officials who have
OL,7,Fendorsed Value Jersey's policies are:
OL,8,FDeputy Gabriel Raimondo (St Brelade),
OL,9,FDeputy Phil Romeril (St John, St
OL,10,FLawrence and Trinity), Deputy Gerald
OL,11,FVoisin (St Helier North), Deputy
OL,12,FSamantha Gleave (St Helier South),
OL,13,FDeputy Robert Parker (St Saviour),
OL,14,FSenator Serena Kersten Guthrie.
OL,16,FPeople First
OL,18,FNewly formed ahead of the 2026
OL,19,Felection, People First says "the
OL,20,Fisland's wealth should be matched by
OL,21,Fsocial decency.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/13
