OL,3,CWhich political groups have performed
OL,4,Cbest in Jersey's Election?
OL,6,F"We believe workers deserve dignity,
OL,7,Frenters deserve security, families
OL,8,Fdeserve support, and every community
OL,9,Fdeserves respect."
OL,11,FThe party only had two candidates,
OL,12,Fboth of whom were unsuccessful in
OL,13,Ftheir attempts to become Deputies of
OL,14,FSt Helier South.
OL,16,FNick le Cornu, People First's leader,
OL,17,Fwas expelled from Reform Jersey in
OL,18,F2014 over tweets he had posted
OL,19,Fregarding Deputy Kristina Moore. He
OL,20,Flater apologised for these comments.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
